'''二(三甲基硅基亚氨基)硫'''是一种[[有机硫化合物|有机硫化合物]]，化学式为S(NSiMe<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>(其中Me为CH<sub>3</sub>），属于[[二亚氨基硫|二亚氨基硫]]类化合物。它是无色液体，可用于合成[[氮化硫|氮化硫]]。例如，它是合成C<sub>2</sub>(N<sub>2</sub>S)<sub>2</sub>的前驱体。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/ic050583j|title=[1,2,5]Thiadiazolo[3,4-c][1,2,5]thiadiazolidyl: A Long-Lived Radical Anion and Its Stable Salts|year=2005|last1=Makarov|first1=Alexander Yu.|last2=Irtegova|first2=Irina G.|last3=Vasilieva|first3=Nadezhda V.|last4=Bagryanskaya|first4=Irina Yu.|last5=Borrmann|first5=Tobias|last6=Gatilov|first6=Yuri V.|last7=Lork|first7=Enno|last8=Mews|first8=Ruediger|last9=Stohrer|first9=Wolf-Dieter|last10=Zibarev|first10=Andrey V.|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=44|issue=20|pages=7194–7199|pmid=16180884}}</ref> 

它可由[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]和[[二(三甲基硅基)氨基钠|二(三甲基硅基)氨基钠]]反应得到：<ref>{{cite journal|title=Synthese eines siliciumorganischen cyclischen Schwefeldiimids (Synthesis of an Organosilicon Cyclic Sulfur Diimide)|journal=Zeitschrift für Naturforschung|year=1970|volume=25B|page=1486-7|doi=10.1515/znb-1970-1240|first1=Otto J.|last1=Scherer|last2=Wies|first2=Reinhard|s2cid=93647579}}</ref>
:SOCl<sub>2</sub>  +  2 NaN(SiMe<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>  → S(NSiMe<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> +  2 NaCl  +  O(SiMe<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>

